# Spacing & Layout System

## Spacing Scale

Use a consistent scale based on 4px/8px:

```css
:root {
  --space-1: 0.25rem;  /* 4px */
  --space-2: 0.5rem;   /* 8px */
  --space-3: 0.75rem;  /* 12px */
  --space-4: 1rem;     /* 16px */
  --space-6: 1.5rem;   /* 24px */
  --space-8: 2rem;     /* 32px */
  --space-12: 3rem;    /* 48px */
  --space-16: 4rem;    /* 64px */
  --space-20: 5rem;    /* 80px */
  --space-32: 8rem;    /* 128px */
}
```

## Content Width

Keep reading columns narrow and focused:

```css
.container {
  max-width: 42rem; /* 672px - optimal reading width */
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

/* Alternative narrower option */
.container-narrow {
  max-width: 40rem; /* 640px */
}
```

## Horizontal Padding

Responsive padding that breathes:

```css
.container {
  padding-left: var(--space-4);   /* 16px mobile */
  padding-right: var(--space-4);
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .container {
    padding-left: var(--space-6);  /* 24px tablet */
    padding-right: var(--space-6);
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .container {
    padding-left: var(--space-12); /* 48px desktop */
    padding-right: var(--space-12);
  }
}
```

## Vertical Rhythm

Consistent section and element spacing:

```css
/* Page-level padding */
main {
  padding-top: var(--space-16);    /* 64px */
  padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  main {
    padding-top: var(--space-32);  /* 128px */
    padding-bottom: var(--space-32);
  }
}

/* Section spacing */
section + section {
  margin-top: var(--space-16); /* 64px between sections */
}

/* Element spacing within sections */
.stack > * + * {
  margin-top: var(--space-4); /* 16px default stack */
}

.stack-lg > * + * {
  margin-top: var(--space-6); /* 24px larger stack */
}
```

## The Horizontal Separator

A refined, understated divider:

```css
.separator {
  width: 3rem;           /* 48px */
  height: 1px;
  background-color: var(--border);
  border-radius: 1px;
  margin-top: var(--space-6);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
}
```

## Gap Utilities

For flexbox and grid layouts:

```css
.gap-sm { gap: var(--space-2); }   /* 8px - tight groupings */
.gap-md { gap: var(--space-4); }   /* 16px - list items */
.gap-lg { gap: var(--space-8); }   /* 32px - card grids */
.gap-xl { gap: var(--space-16); }  /* 64px - major sections */
```

## Common Patterns

```css
/* Hero section */
.hero {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-4);
  padding: var(--space-4);
}

/* Project list */
.project-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-4);
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .project-list {
    gap: var(--space-2); /* Tighter on desktop */
  }
}
```
